title: Foreign national Palestinians will be able to cross into Egypt when border opens to also allow aid into Gaza
description: Foreign national Palestinians will be able to cross the border into Egypt starting at 9 a.m. local time on Monday, a representative for the Embassy of Palestine.

title: Humanitarian crisis grips Gaza
description: A humanitarian crisis is gripping Gaza as hundreds of thousands of displaced Palestinians flee to the south amid the Israeli military’s aerial bombardment in retaliation for Hamas’ brutal terrorist attack one week ago.
